text: Tiniharusamga tyasa belasam'ma sangharsa gardai garnu jabasam'ma ki upadrava samapta humdaina. Ra dharma allahako nimti (pratisthita) nabha'i ja'os. Ra yadi tiniharu sangharsako parityaga gardachan (bhane timi pani parityaga garihala), kinaki atyacari baheka aru kasaimathi atyacara garnu humdaina
